## Architecture

This project uses **Next.js 16 App Router** with `src/` directory convention:

- **src/app/** — Routes, layouts, pages (file-based routing)
- **src/app/layout.tsx** — Root layout with Inter font + globals.css
- **tests/** — Vitest + @testing-library/react

Key conventions:

- Routes are files in `src/app/` — each folder is a route segment
- `layout.tsx` wraps child routes (persists across navigation)
- `page.tsx` is the UI for each route
- API routes go in `src/app/api/` as `route.ts` files
- Shared components go in `src/components/`
- All data fetching is done on the server by default
